import React, { Component } from "react"; import Title from "../../components/General/Title"; export default class AccountLogin extends Component { render() { return (
<form> <div class="form-group"> <label for="exampleInputEmail1"> Email address </label> <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Enter email" /> </div> <div class="form-group"> <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Password</label> <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Password" /> </div> <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"> Submit </button> </form> </div> </React.Fragment> ); } }
